### DB Migration
> [!IMPORTANT]
> Run this SQL against your Supabase database to add the new column:
> ```sql
> ALTER TABLE trades ADD COLUMN IF NOT EXISTS trading_mode TEXT NOT NULL DEFAULT 'paper' CHECK (trading_mode IN ('live', 'paper'));
> ```
